The paper discusses backdoor attacks on deep neural networks, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves transfer learning (cs.LG), image recognition (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper evaluates potential defenses against the attacks, which falls under the category of systems and information theory (cs.SI).
